column5: Caught this one earlier this year. The husky jerk was the ticket and also giving it one last ditch effort before the trip home. My buddy lost one that was quite a bit bigger about 15 minutes earlier.
Now that's a nice lookin gator !!!
Nice pike, looks like it's been eating well.
Nice fish. Im glad that guy is pointing to it or I may have missed it
Nice pike. HJ are my go to pike baits.
nice i love to fish for them
Congrats on the PB jimmer !!!! That's a well fed very healthy beast !!!!! Cheers !!!!
I love fishing for them because I usually don't fish lakes that have pike in them. It's always special when you can target them. Thanks for the comments guys!
Very Nice !!! I wouldn't say no to one of them right about now
Nice fish. Was that one from your trip to QC Jim?
No it wasn't Mike. This one was from the McKeller area.
